    "For BC5CDR, we limit our testing to 1,000 randomly selected samples to minimize computational demands.",
    "Preliminary experiments indicate that model performance on these subsets aligns with results obtained using the full datasets.",
    "Furthermore, we adapt the input context for PolyIE to account for differences in the capabilities of GPT-3.5 and other language models.",
    "For GPT-3.5, we input entire paragraphs, whereas for other LLMs, we broke the paragraphs into sentences and processed them individually, acknowledging their constrained history comprehension and memory abilities.",
    "We report the performance on the test set of each dataset, and the detailed statistics are shown in Table 2."
